   "jp_hex": "15f087432d2f02f0e0f4c434f5bc3700f19b1c1748f2461c0cf29d0d2b060000",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e9e7b9e7da02e7e9e828e918e834e903ef29e85defb6e824ef31e7b4e98be9940200e7c5e8c10ce83ee7c90def970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12b8",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}『チーム』について",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}关于队伍",
   "jp_hex": "15010101010cf29d0d34f0ab2f0000",
   "zh_hex": "1501010101e8bbe879e7c9ec070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12c7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "複数のユニットを同じマスに配置した{00}状態を『チーム』と呼びます",
   "zh_text": "把多个单位、配置在同一格里的状态、称{00}为『小队』",
   "jp_hex": "15f5bc37f19b4cf0e0f4c434f2af232a00f2464c0cf29d0d31e1fae058f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be7e9e828e918e83402ea34ea0eef29e85defb6e824ef31e7b4e98be99402ea0100e7c10ce83ee7c90d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12e8",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "『チーム』は最大3機までで、配置した{00}ユニットが同時に行動や戦闘を行えます",
   "zh_text": "『小队』最多由3台组成、队内单位、可{00}同时行动和战斗",
   "jp_hex": "150cf29d0d38f2f51092f02b3002f2af232a00f19b1cf30e34f0e343f04f4c9f19f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "150ce83ee7c90de8c5e7e9e8a6ef60ea16ea0de83702e7c9e99ae918e83402e7c400e85def2defd6ef30e7d3ef28e7ff000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x130d",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "また『チーム攻撃』を選ぶことで{00}敵全体への攻撃も可能になります",
   "zh_text": "此外、选择『小队攻击』、还能对敌方全{00}体、发动攻击",
   "jp_hex": "15f09e0cf29df01f0d4ce39ae05af0023000c3f9383b37f01f41f169343347f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e966eaaa0ce83ee7c9ef67e7cc0d02e7f7e7c6e7bee7e3efb1efb400ef4f02e870ef30ef67e7cc00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1355",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "罗贝托·卡帕",
   "jp_text": "こうすれば一回の戦闘に{00}複数のユニットが参加できる！！",
   "zh_text": "只要这样、一场战斗里、就能让多台机体{00}一同上阵！！",
   "jp_hex": "15f087f16639f91a37f04f3400f5bc37f19b1cf3bcf0174806060000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b9e7da02efb6e876ef28e7ffef3102e7c5e7c6e7f9e7e9ea16e7e4ef4f00efb6e85def4ceb48ef97ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1371",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "罗贝托·卡帕",
   "jp_text": "いいか、見てろ……！",
   "zh_text": "听好了、看清楚……！",
   "jp_hex": "1517171b029a2f4a0909060000",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7c7e7ba02e7f6e995ebd30909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13a3",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "罗贝托·卡帕",
   "jp_text": "戦闘はこの『チーム』で戦うのが基本だ",
   "zh_text": "战斗、基本上就是靠这个『小队』来进行{00}的",
   "jp_hex": "15f04f38f0050cf29d0d30b918371cf5722b0000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ff02e829efa6ef4ce7c5e7b6e8c7e7b9e8280ce83ee7c90defcfe892efd600e7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13dc",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "阿波利",
   "jp_text": "じゃあ、次は攻撃の方法……",
   "zh_text": "那么、接下来是攻击的方法……",
