   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b402e9a7e7b8e7bbe7d8e8eae84e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e55",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "西玛·加拉霍",
   "jp_text": "じゃあ、もう一回チャンスを{00}あげようじゃないか",
   "zh_text": "那么、就再给你们一次机会吧",
   "jp_hex": "15f0cb02f02af91af4394c00f2b6f007244233171b0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e80be839e7b8e7bbefb6e864e7e4e7e2e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e91",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "どうかね、シーマ中佐？",
   "zh_text": "怎么样、西玛中佐？",
   "jp_hex": "15f1293602f08ff0a0050000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7da02e7f8e845ef4eefba0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e9d",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "我々の実力は理解してもらえたかな？",
   "zh_text": "我们的实力、您应该已经有所了解了吧？",
   "jp_hex": "15f01837f4a838f2fb232ff04019f03d33050000",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4e87fefb002e835e873e898ef3ae8b7e7cbe7fbe7bae89de7bae7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1edd",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "西玛·加拉霍",
   "jp_text": "まだ、これくらいじゃあ、{00}背中を預ける気にはなれないね",
   "zh_text": "光凭这点程度、还不足以让我、把后背交{00}托给你们呢",
   "jp_hex": "15f06202f00ef1a8f0cb0200f66f4cf347489334f03a493317360000",
   "zh_hex": "15e83dea49e7b9e822ea7de96d02e7f7e7b5ea1ee7f3e7f9efcc02e81be7fee9e4e86100e7f4e839e7b8e7bbe90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "西玛·加拉霍",
   "jp_text": "戦いには他にもいろんな{00}要素があるんだ",
   "zh_text": "战斗里、可还有着、各种各样的要素呢",
   "jp_hex": "15b9173438e3d83441174a4d3300fa761cf00f4d2b0000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ffef3102e7c4e7f7e7cbe86d02e819e7d1e819e7dae7b4ef2aec86e90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f10",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "西玛·加拉霍",
   "jp_text": "そいつらに、どう対応するかってのも{00}見せてもらわないとねえ……",
   "zh_text": "你们要怎么去应对那些、也得让我好好瞧{00}瞧才行……",
   "jp_hex": "15f2cc463402f053f57ff004f3b6374100f0da2ff0404b33173136e04d09090000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbef2ae7f2e7bde7ebe873e7bee7b7e8a402e7c0e80ae7f9efcce7c7e7c7ead400ead4e836efd6090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f4c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "では、いったん休{SLOT:2031}を教んで{00}演習続行ということにしよう",
   "zh_text": "那么、就先稍作休整、然后继续演习吧",
   "jp_hex": "15f00a02fb43e16ee70f4ce18e4d3000f472f9aa311718f0023423f0070000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5ef8bead5ef2fe90ee9fe02e7efe7fee9d6e9adea2feab6e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "シーマ中佐もそれでいいかな？",
   "zh_text": "西玛中佐、这样、可以吧？",
