  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2009",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "……そうか",
   "zh_text": "……是吗",
   "jp_hex": "150909f0091b0000",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2011",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "では、こちらも出撃する部隊を{00}『編成』しておく必要があるな",
   "zh_text": "那么、我们这边也得、把出击的部队『编{00}成』好才行",
   "jp_hex": "15f00a02f07a41f110f004f0644c000cf4490d232f1a1ef0b51cf00f330000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbe7b9e899e7c0e80a02e81befbee7cce7b4ef70e7c90cec8900e8370de7c7e836efd60000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2063",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}{01}『編成と出撃』",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}{01}编成",
   "jp_hex": "1501010101010cf44931f1100d0000",
   "zh_hex": "150101010101ec89e8370000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2072",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "ステージにユニットを出撃させるには{00}予め『編成』を行わなければなりません",
   "zh_text": "要让单位在关卡中出击、必须事先进行{00}『编成』",
   "jp_hex": "15f43834f19b4cf110f02e48343800d6400cf4490d4c9f4b331f493933473d274d0000",
