   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7feea16e966e918ef4e02e966eaaa0cec89e8370de7cde7fe09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ae",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "この『編成』画面に切り替わります",
   "zh_text": "就会切换到这个『编成』画面",
   "jp_hex": "15f0050cf4490df82d34fdcd47f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2ef3fea78e7d7e7b9e8280cec89e8370decefe8620000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20bf",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "ここで出撃させたいユニットを{00}戦艦に搭載し、パイロットを配属します",
   "zh_text": "在这里、把想出击的单位、搭载到战舰上{00}、并为其配属驾驶员",
