   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9ef3102e81be7e6efbee7cce7b4e918e83402eb09eb1de7d7ef28e7d4ef4c0002e957e7c1e8cfea34ea24e953e975e84900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20de",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "『編成』が終了したら{00}次は実際の『出撃』となります",
   "zh_text": "『编成』完成后、接下来、就是实际的{00}『出击』了",
   "jp_hex": "150cf4490d1cf3ae232a4600e29f38f4a7370cf1100df395f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "150cec89e8370de87ee837e7fe02efceef4defcf02e7c5e7b6e87fedc3e7b4000cefbee7cc0de7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20fa",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "バックステージの『作戦』で{00}『進撃』を選択すると……",
   "zh_text": "在后台的『作战』中、选择『进击』之后{00}……",
   "jp_hex": "15f6dff438370cf0e40d30000cf8af0d4cf3b0f0f909090000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7feea16e7b40cef2fef280def4e02e966eaaa0ce892e7cc0de7cde7fe000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2116",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "この『出撃』画面に切り替わります",
   "zh_text": "就会切换到这个『出击』画面",
   "jp_hex": "15f0050cf1100df82d34fdcd47f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2ef3fea78e7d7e7b9e8280cefbee7cc0decefe862000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2127",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "ここで『Aボタン』を押せば{00}次ステージへと進みます",
   "zh_text": "在这里、按下『A键』、便会进入下一关",
   "jp_hex": "15f03e300ce01cfa920d4ce0cb273900e29ff4383b31e33f3ef0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9ef3102ea76ef4d0cea9ceb710d02e8fae7e2e892e891ef4defb6e8bb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x215b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛利根",
   "jp_text": "補艦の方はもう用意できていますので、",
   "zh_text": "母舰已经准备好了、",
   "jp_hex": "15f55837d038f02af216f0172ff029253730020000",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d5e7d4ef3ae8b7e87ae877e7c7e7ba02000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2170",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛利根",
   "jp_text": "後はユニットとパイロットを{00}戦艦に配属してください",
   "zh_text": "剩下、就请把机体和驾驶员、编入战舰里{00}吧",
   "jp_hex": "159c38f19b31f0ba4c00f15e34f755232ff083170000",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3aef4d02e7c5e83ae81be7e4ef4fe7d3e953e975e84902ec89e891ef28e7d4ef3100e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21a1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "了解だ、マリガン",
   "zh_text": "了解了、玛利根",
   "jp_hex": "15f0862b02f39c0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bae89de7ba02e845e82ee9b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d96",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "布莱特·诺亚",
   "jp_text": "これまでの戦い、ご苦漏",
