   "jp_hex": "15f00ef02b37b91702f6420000",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5da3",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "布莱特·诺亚",
   "jp_text": "この「宇宙世紀ルート」を最後まで{00}遊んでくれて感射する",
   "zh_text": "感谢你陪『宇宙世纪路线』一路走到了最{00}后",
   "jp_hex": "15f005e00bf0a8f695fb35e00c4cf145f02b00e5ae4d30f0152ff288f0040000",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8ef420ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2e890e7d7e7bae8c500e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5dc3",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "布莱特·诺亚",
   "jp_text": "なお、ロンド·ベル隊の戦いは{00}ここでひとまず終了するが……",
   "zh_text": "隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就先在此告一段落{00}……",
   "jp_hex": "15f29002f17a04f0f4bd37b9173800f03e30f9fcf15bf3aef0041c09090000",
   "zh_hex": "15ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a0009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5de2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "布莱特·诺亚",
   "jp_text": "ケーム自体はまだ続けることが可能だ{00}この後も引き続きを楽しんで雷しい",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请尽情享{00}受下去",
   "jp_hex": "15f763f702f0ea2bf13048f0021cf1692b00f0059c41f429e3d01d4cf5d64d30f252170000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae8f2e88bec0600e8c8ef4de7eb000000000000000000"
